p: Office of the Sheriff of King County W.T.}SS.

I William Cochrane Sheriff of King County W.T. do hereby certify that on the 23d day of May A.D. 1887 I received the writ of Habeas corpus a true copy of which is hereto annexed; and personally served the same on the same day on Ella Cline, she being the person named in said writ, by delivering to and leaving with her personally in Seattle King County W.T. said writ of Habeas Corpus.
Dated at Seattle King Co W.T. this 24th day of May 1887
